### GET STRATEGIES
GET {{host}}/investment/strategies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### CREATE INVESTMENT PROPOSAL
POST {{host}}/investment/proposal/{{group_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": "50",
  "strategy_id": "e3f21026-7923-4efa-a917-6801558a00b2",
  "currency_id": "33de6c7c-62a2-4182-813a-9005183be70d"
}

### EXECUTE INVESTMENT PROPOSAL
POST {{host}}/investment/execute/{{group_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "proposal_id": "40ab35cc-713b-49d8-bec4-11cacb7fb0ca"
}

### GET INVESTMENTS
GET {{host}}/investment/{{group_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### WITHDRAW INVESTMENT (matured = full NAV; active = ragequit with fee)
POST {{host}}/investment/withdraw/{{group_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "investment_id": "97f7da58-f522-4a0c-8207-2e0b42efb9b5"
}

### NOTE
# - Strategies with valuation_mode=mark_to_market create holdings at execute.
# - Pulse revalues MTM positions with PRICE_ORACLE_MODE=mock|live.
# - Ragequit (admin, active only): payout = NAV * (1 - ragequit_fee_bps/10000); fee burned.

### GET SNAPSHOTS
GET {{host}}/investment/97f7da58-f522-4a0c-8207-2e0b42efb9b5/snapshots
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}